# 🧑‍💼 Employee Management System (C-based Client-Server)

This is a basic **Client-Server Employee Management System** written in **C**, using a custom message-based communication model with **hashing** for efficient storage and retrieval of employee data.

---

## 📋 Features

* Add new employee records
* Delete existing employee records
* Get individual employee details by ID
* Modify employee data (partially or completely)
* Display all employee records
* Uses **hash tables** for efficient storage
* Simulates **client-server** message passing


## ⚙️ Requirements

* GCC Compiler (Linux or Windows)
* Basic knowledge of C programming
* Terminal for compilation and execution

---

